{"tid":818163,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人老豆愈大愈on9?","createTime":"2018-09-14T02:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-14T07:16:30.000Z","uid":123991,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ab0ba77940755e2757449d66e3cbbbcb918e3f41","tid":818163,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"唉.. 都估唔到佢會變成咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前後生果陣佢仲好醒<br />\n隔晚就劈酒屌女傾生意<br />\n星期六日一早去皮車<br />\n一直都視佢為磅樣<br />\n自從退左休之後太好得閒<br />\n本身屋企有個 whatsapp group<br />\n掃完地又影張相send上group <br />\n好似個師奶咁樓下買左個瓜又send上黎話好抵<br />\n耐唔耐又send d 內容農產場post<br />\nd 垃圾大陸 video 等等<br />\n覆到都唔知覆佢咩好<br />\n啱先又問收埋喺梳化件發泡膠去左邊<br />\n屌佢老母邊有人收埋件發泡膠喺底又唔單聲, 跟住話有用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (梗緊比我執屋果陣丟咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n喺屋企睇電視又好似呀叔咁指住個電視黎鬧<br />\n之前同佢去旅行又成日邊度唔去果度唔去咁, 成日想返香港<br />\n到我夾硬諗搵d野講想分享我做左d乜<br />\n差唔多次次一係就話危險, 一係就話哂錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌佢老母我突登搵topic同佢講都仲要比佢gut<br />\n對住佢真係愈黎愈燥<br />\n而家唯有夾硬講d飯幾好食, d湯幾好飲咁啦d無營養對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b051342d58cf55e36e4491ae2408524a4aba5a","tid":818163,"uid":208364,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:29:10.000Z","msg":"更年期"},{"pid":"b8558a8a0651f92f06798d38ee82aa3f4445bcb5","tid":818163,"uid":25900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"我老豆都係<br />\n成鳩日懶醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2895f72cdf5293a00666f80ebb6df8fb3415bcf","tid":818163,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b8558a8a0651f92f06798d38ee82aa3f4445bcb5","tid":818163,"uid":25900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T02:30:49.000Z","msg":"我老豆都係<br />\n成鳩日懶醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy